      "Spellcasting": {
        "description": "You get spellcasting abilities at level 1. Your spellcasting ability is Intelligence, so your spell save DC = 8 + your proficiency bonus + your Intelligence modifier and your spell attack modifier = your proficiency bonus + your Intelligence modifier. You can prepare a number of spells equal to your wizard level plus your Intelligence modifier. You can also cast spells that you have in your spellbook as rituals if it has the ritual tag."
